<abstract abstract-type="short" xml:lang="en"><p><![CDATA[AbstractThis paper focuses on the centrality of hair in body aesthetics investments in the studied context. Since hair has a major role in the aesthetic building of the body, the article seeks to understand the meanings of these practices based on local understandings of the body.]]></p></abstract>
